search: | localop | inputlookup dmc_assets | stats dc(serverName) as instance_count dc(machine) as machine_count by search_group | where match(search_group,"dmc_group_") | eval count = "count" | chart format=$VAL$_$AGG$ values(instance_count) AS instance_count values(machine_count) AS machine_count over count by search_group

| inputlookup dmc_assets | join type=outer serverName [ | rest splunk_server_group=dmc_group_* /services/server/status/resource-usage/hostwide | eval cpu_pct = cpu_system_pct + cpu_user_pct | eval mem_used_pct = mem_used / mem * 100 | fields cpu_pct mem_used_pct splunk_server | rename splunk_server as serverName ] | join type=outer peerURI [ | rest splunk_server=local /services/search/distributed/peers | fields title status | rename title as peerURI ] | eval status=if(((status!="Up") OR isnull(status)) AND (peerURI!="localhost"), 1, 0) | stats dc(serverName) as instances dc(machine) as machines sum(status) as num_down avg(cpu_pct) as cpu avg(mem_used_pct) as mem by search_group | eval cpu=round(cpu, 2) | eval mem=round(mem, 2)
| rest splunk_server_group=dmc_group_cluster_master /services/cluster/master/peers
| rest splunk_server_group=dmc_group_cluster_master /services/cluster/master/indexes
